&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://cicur.github.io/p/ubuntu-22.04-lts-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85windows-10-%E5%8F%8C%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/Disk_2.png&#34;
